sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway/Envoy Proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant BBR as Body Based Router<br/>9004/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelPod as Model Server Pod<br/>(vLLM/SGLang/Triton)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 1: Inference Request Processing

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Gateway-defined
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 TLS<br/>Request headers + body
    BBR->>BBR: Parse body, extract<br/>"model" field
    BBR-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>Add X-Gateway-Model-Name header

    Note over Gateway,EPP: Gateway routes based on model header

    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 TLS<br/>Headers with model name
    EPP->>EPP: Scheduling Pipeline:<br/>Filter → Score → Pick<br/>(KV cache, queue depth,<br/>prefix cache, LoRA)
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>Set target-endpoint:<br/>pod-ip:port

    Gateway->>ModelPod: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>Cluster internal

    ModelPod-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over EPP,ModelPod: Flow 2: Metrics Collection (continuous)

    loop Every 50ms (configurable)
        EPP->>ModelPod: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (configurable TLS)<br/>No auth
        ModelPod-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics<br/>(kv_cache_usage, queue_depth,<br/>running_requests, lora_info)
    end

    Note over Prometheus,EPP: Flow 3: EPP Metrics Exposition

    Prometheus->>EPP: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/9090<br/>Optional: Bearer Token<br/>(TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview)
    EPP-->>Prometheus: EPP scheduling metrics

    Note over BBR,K8sAPI: Flow 4: BBR ConfigMap Reconciliation

    BBR->>K8sAPI: Watch ConfigMaps<br/>label: bbr-managed=true<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>BBR: ConfigMap updates<br/>(adapter→base-model mappings)

    Note over EPP,K8sAPI: Flow 5: CRD Reconciliation (continuous)

    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool,<br/>InferenceObjective,<br/>InferenceModelRewrite, Pods<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Resource events<br/>(create/update/delete)
